{"tid":130102,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【心郁做爸爸？】抱住老友囝囝情深對望 許志安父愛滿瀉","createTime":"2017-02-22T06:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T00:44:56.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"009c7ab189a0bf7439b9cb607e105a89953f584e","tid":130102,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170222/s00007/ed13ea85f318b5db30028661c1b7b535.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170222%2Fs00007%2Fed13ea85f318b5db30028661c1b7b535.jpg&h=81f3b966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭秀文（Sammi）日前接受訪問時，談及借種產子話題，Sammi表示對未肯定生BB的女性而言，雪卵是最好的方法，她笑言要雪就現在雪，再不雪就無得雪，至於是否生育，Sammi在訪問中表示自己也未肯定。<br />\n<br />\nSammi雖未肯定是否做媽咪，但許志安就肯定「父愛滿瀉」，事緣安仔與老友王傲山一家三口飯叙，安仔見到王傲山兒子時，父愛爆棚，還情深對望，安仔流露滿意笑容，王傲山在網上留言：「On BB with real Bb」，而安仔亦在Instagram上載大手牽小手照片：並說：「Touched」，未知許氏夫婦會否考慮生番個BB呢？<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170222/s00007/1487744071713#sthash.OhuGyd1E.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170222%2Fs00007%2F1487744071713%23sthash.OhuGyd1E.dpuf&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=9336b07f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170222%2Fs00007%2F1487744071713%23sthash.OhuGyd1E.dpuf&h=2ceb2924\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170222/s00007/1487744071713#sthash.OhuGyd1E.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"9d3284a41e0958feef9e391d27ac8674b8c1e1aa","tid":130102,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T08:20:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155dfa770cec9ce953cfa3ea834e16f7835e6280","tid":130102,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img